data.description: Embrace the expansive living experience on 40 acres of tranquility! This residence is conveniently situated just down Bergemann Rd, offering easy access to town while providing ample privacy. As you step into the home, a spacious living room welcomes you, setting the tone for the generous proportions found throughout. Flowing seamlessly from the living room, the dining room and kitchen create a warm and inviting space. A small breakfast nook on the other side of the kitchen adds a charming touch. The master bedroom, centrally located in the home, features an attached 5-piece bath and a walk-in closet for your comfort. Venture down the hall to discover two more bedrooms and a 3/4 bath, providing well-appointed living spaces. Additionally, an office and a small family room/den offer versatile options and could easily be converted into additional bedrooms to suit your needs. The laundry room serves double duty as a mudroom, offering practical entry points into the house. Behind the residence, a detached two-car garage and a spacious Quonset hut with concrete floors provide ample space for a workshop, storage, or additional enclosed parking. Surrounded by 40 rolling acres, this property beckons you to bring your horses and live the Western dream. Revel in the breathtaking 360-degree mountain views that paint the backdrop of this unique and expansive setting. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home and experience the beauty of country living. Schedule your viewing today!
